    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Chainwarden enforcers are the elite heavy infantry of the Warden companies — armored veterans who hold the line while lighter troops press the attack. They carry chain-maces capable of controlling the battlefield and respond to pressure with Stand Fast, digging in rather than retreating. Their Overwhelm bonus action lets them pin down multiple opponents at once. An enforcer platoon is nearly impossible to dislodge from a fortified position.</p>",
